OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FAccording to the latest National and
OL,7,Fstate polls, concerns about
OL,8,Fimmigration are one of, if not the
OL,9,Fbiggest concern for ahead of the
OL,10,FPresidential election in less than
OL,11,Fnine months.
OL,13,FEagle Pass is a small Texas border
OL,14,Fcity in the Del Rio sector. It has
OL,15,Fbeen known to be an epicenter for
OL,16,Fmigrant crossings.
OL,18,FThe town of about 30,000 people has
OL,19,Fbecome a major corridor for illegal
OL,20,Fcrossings in recent years.
