OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FThe small town has become known for
OL,7,Fits razor wire fences attempting to
OL,8,Fprevent migrant crossing, shipping
OL,9,Fcontainers acting as a make-shift
OL,10,Fbarrier, and rotational patrols of the
OL,11,FTexas National Guard.
OL,13,FIt's also at the heart of a state and
OL,14,Ffederal clash over border security.
OL,16,FIn January, the state of Texas took
OL,17,Fcontrol of Shelby Park on the banks of
OL,18,FRio Grande, Eagle Pass.
