OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FSince then, there has been a feud
OL,7,Fbetween Texas' Republican governor and
OL,8,Fthe Democratic White House.
OL,10,FIn Eagle Pass, Texas armed militia are
OL,11,Fnow patrolling the border, as migrants
OL,12,Fcontinue to cross from Mexico into the
OL,13,FUnited States.
OL,15,FPatriots for America is a conservative
OL,16,FChristian militia trying to stop human
OL,17,Ftrafficking and drug crime, based in
OL,18,FNorth Texas.
