OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FThe militia was formed in 2015, and
OL,7,Fthey helped people get their cars to
OL,8,Frallies.
OL,10,FLater in 2019, the group began a new
OL,11,Ffocus on combating child sex
OL,12,Ftrafficking.
OL,14,FAnd then in 2021, the PFA started its
OL,15,Fbig border missions - continuing to
OL,16,Fprevent human trafficking and limiting
OL,17,Fthe operation of drug cartels on the
OL,18,Fborder.
