OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FThe group has attracted members not
OL,7,Fjust in Texas, but in Florida,
OL,8,FIllinois, and Michigan.
OL,10,FThe militia claims nearly 2,000
OL,11,Fmembers nationwide, although exact
OL,12,Ffigures are not available due to
OL,13,Fsecurity concerns.
OL,15,FThe members patrol the river at
OL,16,Fvarious times of day, trace migrants
OL,17,Fthrough carrizo cane, and carry night-
OL,18,Fvision equipment.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
