OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FThe group has also had permission from
OL,7,Flandowners on the border for their
OL,8,Fcause.
OL,10,FOverall, illegal crossings along the
OL,11,FUS-Mexico border have declined since a
OL,12,Frecord high in December 2023.
OL,14,FIn January, Border Patrol recorded a
OL,15,Fhigh 125,000 migrant apprehensions in
OL,16,Fbetween ports of entry along the
OL,17,Fsouthern border, compared to nearly
OL,18,F250,000 in December.
