OL,3,CHow a Texas Militia group patrol the
OL,4,Cborder as migrants cross from Mexico
OL,6,FThe PFA's actions and behavior have
OL,7,Fcaused concern among Human Rights
OL,8,Fgroups.
OL,10,FThe American Civil Liberties Union of
OL,11,FTexas has been particularly critical
OL,12,Fof the group.
OL,14,FThey claim the group has been
OL,15,Fpatrolling the border without
OL,16,Ftraining, questioning migrants, and
OL,17,Fdetaining them.
