OL,6,FThe PFA has denied any accusations of
OL,7,FWhite Supremacy, racism, violence, or
OL,8,Fintimidation towards migrants. The
OL,9,Ffounder, Samuel Hall says the group is
OL,10,Ffaith-based, Christ-centred - and a
OL,11,Fpeaceful organisation.
